  "field_meaning": "daily MAX of hourly temperature_2m_previous_dayN over the local calendar day = the daily-high FORECAST at lead N days (previous_day1 ~24h-ahead, previous_day2 ~48h-ahead); multiple rows per event (one per lead), as-of join handles the revision toward shorter lead naturally",
